{"product_id":"rahua-shampoo","title":"RAHUA SHAMPOO","description":"\u003ch5\u003e\u003cem\u003eDescription\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/h5\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003eAs Seen In: \u003cem\u003eVogue\u003c\/em\u003e, \u003cem\u003eInStyle\u003c\/em\u003e \u0026amp; \u003cem\u003eMadame \u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 100% natural, organic, responsibly harvested light-lather shampoo creates and maintains healthy, bouncy and lustrous hair. It works for all hair types and is especially effective for color-treated hair. A natural cleanser derived from coconut oil cleanses gently without removing color pigmentation, while Rahua oil molecules penetrate deep into the hair shaft, strengthening and fortifying weak, damaged strands while regenerating the scalp and hair follicles.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eOur Beauty Notes\u003c\/em\u003e: We don't believe in washing our hair daily, but every 2-3 days we lather up with clean, organic shampoo that doesn't strip our hair of its color. This was designed around colored treated hair and with the addition of coconut oil to hydrate those chemically treated stands into deep nourishment. \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cem\u003eUse\u003c\/em\u003e\n\u003c\/h5\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Apply on thoroughly wet hair to begin shampoo and work into a lather. Rinse and follow with Rahua Conditioner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eComplementing products: Rahua Conditioner, Omega 9 Hair Mask and Finishing Treatment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch5\u003e\u003cem\u003eIngredients\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/h5\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"short-description clear\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"std\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"prod_ingredients\"\u003eStar Ingredients (Full List Coming Soon) \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"prod_ingredients\"\u003eRAHUA-UNGURAHUA - fortifies weak, damaged strands while nourishing and regenerating the scalp and hair follicles.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003ePALO SANTO - “holy wood” is Rahua’s signature scent, which offers a delicate fragrance; the ingredient also provides a soothing aromatherapy experience while shampooing.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eQUINOA - gluten free super-food that revitalizes hair and promotes healing and moisture retention.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eCOCONUT AND SHEA BUTTER BETAINES - safely, gently and effectively remove oil and dirt without stripping necessary nutrients.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Rahua","offers":[{"title":"Shampoo","offer_id":1157620728,"sku":"","price":32.0,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0731\/0835\/products\/SHAMPOO_Rahua.jpg?v=1485379528","url":"https:\/\/levertbeauty.com\/products\/rahua-shampoo","provider":"LeVert Beauty","version":"1.0","type":"link"}